姦甚至輪姦，早前在中大對話會上發言的女學生吳傲雪亦指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">最少六人曾在新屋嶺受性侵或虐待</span>，其中<span style=\"color: red;\">一名男生更遭不止一名警員雞姦</span>，他仍在考慮是否站出來公開經歷。風雨蘭創辦人兼資深法醫馬宣立坦言，強姦案取證絕非容易，但鼓勵受害人向可信任的人求助，讓知情人事「有個大picture（局勢）」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191014/6IW2YHJHD4QB5J4EEBHP64W4LU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191014%2F6IW2YHJHD4QB5J4EEBHP64W4LU%2F&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX%2F4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=79405cf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191014%2F6IW2YHJHD4QB5J4EEBHP64W4LU%2F&h=ebcbf481\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191014/6IW2YHJHD4QB5J4EEBHP64W4LU/</a>"},{"pid":"70e0c48cf28871c0ccab19122481568cfac28dfc","tid":1696636,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d102471c42b23a3b07a14169c4f9e67d8274df2","tid":1696636,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a374a8667ee9472682c42cd9783d974fb7af923","tid":1696636,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"唔知神通廣大嘅老豆搵唔搵到新屋嶺啲仔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"應該搵唔到 因為都唔係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"香港曱甴同大陸曱甴都有可能啦<br />\n一樣冇人性可言 完全冇分別<br />\n唔好覺得香港品種嘅做唔出先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">定絲打你知道啲野</span>"}]}